<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>IsFor Pusat Riset Informatika</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    <style>
      @keyframes float {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%,
        100% {
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
        50% {
          opacity: 0.8;
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideInLeft {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateX(-50px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideInRight {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateX(50px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      .animate-float {
        animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .animate-slide-left {
        animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      }

      .animate-slide-right {
        animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      }

      .swiss-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .swiss-grid {
          gap: 2rem;
        }
      }

      .typography-display {
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      }

      .typography-body {
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        transform-origin: center;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
      }

      .illustration-wrapper {
        position: relative;
      }

      .illustration-wrapper::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -10%;
        right: -10%;
        width: 70%;
        height: 70%;
        background: #3b82f6;
        opacity: 0.1;
        border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
        z-index: -1;
        animation: pulse 10s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes blob {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
        }
        25% {
          transform: translate(20px, -20px) scale(1.1);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9);
        }
        75% {
          transform: translate(20px, 20px) scale(1.1);
        }
      }

      .animate-blob {
        animation: blob 7s infinite;
      }

      .animation-delay-2000 {
        animation-delay: 2s;
      }
    </style>
    <!-- VISI DAN MISI -->
  </head>
  <section id="visi-misi" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-12">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">
          Visi & Misi
        </h1>
        <div class="w-12 md:w-16 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Vision Card -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md border-2 border-blue-700 max-h-56 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 animate-fade-in"
        >
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3 md:mb-4">
            Visi
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
            Menjadi pusat unggulan dalam pengembangan teknologi Internet of
            Things (IoT) yang inovatif dan berkelanjutan untuk meningkatkan
            kualitas hidup manusia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission Card -->
        <div
          class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md border-2 border-blue-700 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 animate-fade-in-up"
        >
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3 md:mb-4">
            Misi
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 md:space-y-4">
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              1. Melakukan riset mendalam tentang teknologi IoT untuk
              peningkatan kualitas hidup manusia.
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              2. Mengembangkan prototipe IoT inovatif dan bernilai tinggi untuk
              kebutuhan masyarakat.
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              3. Membangun kolaborasi dengan akademisi, industri, pemerintah,
              dan masyarakat.
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              4. Menyelenggarakan pelatihan IoT bagi mahasiswa, dosen, dan
              masyarakat umum.
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              5. Mempublikasikan hasil riset dan memperoleh hak kekayaan
              intelektual.
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600">
              6. Berkontribusi dalam pengembangan kebijakan IoT di Indonesia.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</html>
